===Verb===
'''[[home]] [[in]] [[on]]'''
#{{idiom}} To [[focus]] or [[narrow]] down to something; to [[find]] or draw closer, as by [[trial]] and [[error]] or a gradual [[seeking]] process.
#:''He used the clues to '''home in on''' the source of the flames.''
